-- Teloxim Wins Contract for Water-Network Upgrade Near Bucharest
-- B y   I r i n a   S a v u
-- 2013-05-23T14:46:03Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-05-23/teloxim-wins-contract-for-water-network-upgrade-near-bucharest.html
Teloxim CON SRL, a construction
company in  Romania , won a 23.2 million-lei ($6.9 million)
contract from local utility Apa-Canal Ilfov SA to upgrade water
networks near the capital city of Bucharest.  Apa-Canal Ilfov received nine offers for the contract,
which was initially valued at 25.7 million lei and includes
water and sewage infrastructure upgrades in the southern town of
Pantelimon, according to  a notice  published on the European
